Field,Your data,Notes
Name,Max Mustermann,Your full name. Used to sign the emails.
City,Berlin,Your city name. Appears in the email body.
Zip code,12345,Your postal code. Used to search for nearby therapists.
Insurance type,public,"Accepted values: 'gesetzlich' or 'public' for public insurance; 'privat' or 'private' for private insurance."
Insurance company,TK (Techniker Krankenkasse),The name of your health insurance provider.
Symptoms,Depression and anxiety,Brief description of your symptoms. This appears in the email body.
Previous diagnosis,"Generalized Anxiety Disorder, ADHD",Optional. Your diagnosis code if you have one. Leave blank if not applicable.
Your email,max.mustermann@gmail.com,Optional. Used in the protocol document only — not sent automatically.
Number of therapists,20,How many therapists to contact. 20-30 is recommended for Kostenerstattung.
Email language,German,"Language for the outreach emails. Accepted values: 'German' or 'English' (case insensitive). Leave blank to default to German."
Availability,available now,"Optional. Options: 'available now', 'up to 3 months', 'over 3 months', 'over 12 months'. Leave blank for no filter."
Insurance filter,,"Optional. Options: 'public' (GKV), 'private' (PKV), 'kostenerstattung', 'self-pay'. Leave blank for no filter."
Foreign therapy language,,"Optional. Only needed if you want therapy in a language other than German. Examples: 'English', 'Persian', 'Turkish', 'Russian'. See docs/therapie_de_filter_params.md for all options."
Therapy format,,"Optional. Options: 'individual', 'group', 'family', 'couples', 'children'. Leave blank for no filter."
Focus / topic,,"Optional. The main topic you want to work on. Examples: 'depression', 'anxiety', 'trauma', 'ADHD', 'burnout'. See docs/therapie_de_filter_params.md for all options."
Therapist gender,,"Optional. Options: 'female', 'male', 'non-binary'. Leave blank for no preference."
